{#
  Manuscript index page.

  Spine overview: parts as summary cards with chapter range
  and type breakdown. Full chapter lists live on part pages.

  Context:
    parts: list of part context dicts (with number_min/max, non_prose_types)
    unassigned_chapters: list of chapter dicts
    unassigned_scenes: list of scene dicts
    top_characters: list of dicts (name, role, metrics)
    max_name_len: int for name padding alignment
    character_count: int total
    chapter_status_counts: dict of status -> count
    scene_status_counts: dict of status -> count
#}
# Manuscript

